    "spell_type": "focus",
    "rank": 4,
    "text": "With the threat of more pain, you compel a creature you've recently harmed. You issue a command to the target, with the effects of the spell *command*. If the target is frightened, stupefied, or taking persistent damage, it takes a \u20132 circumstance penalty to the save. Regardless of the result, the target is then temporarily immune for 1 hour.",
